&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-flickr-embed=&#34;true&#34;  href=&#34;https://www.flickr.com/photos/98699716@N08/32512186912/in/photostream/&#34; title=&#34;DSC05889.JPG&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/544/32512186912_1af829356f_z.jpg&#34; width=&#34;640&#34; height=&#34;426&#34; alt=&#34;DSC05889.JPG&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;script async src=&#34;//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js&#34; charset=&#34;utf-8&#34;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;신규&#34;&gt;신규&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Arduino Pro Mini&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;L293D&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RGB Led&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RF 315Mhz Receiver&lt;/li&gt;
